  "2026-07-21T03:38:19.888Z",maintainer-agent,"Verification evidence 2026-07-21: full sandboxed coverage passed 324 files / 6038 tests at exact 100/100/100/100 (statements 40605/40605, branches 28585/28585, functions 8240/8240, lines 39504/39504). pnpm lint passed: ESLint 0 warnings, jscpd 0 clones, static-quality (100% docstrings incl. exported+member, complexity), package-boundary, token-budget (14 surfaces). Contracts snapshot regenerated. Manual dogfood in a temp workspace built a diamond+shortcut ordering DAG and confirmed pm graph slack (makespan 4, shortcut task slack 1, critical path A->B->C->D), pm graph centrality (betweenness ranking with directed fan-in/out), and pm graph articulation (correctly reports zero cuts on the biconnected diamond). New unit specs: scheduling.spec.ts (7), centrality.spec.ts (12); integration in run.spec.ts (+3). All three subcommands verified across CLI human + --json + --summary output."
